data.title: Former Canadian prime minister Lester B. Pearson is buried at MacLaren Cemetery in Wakefield. (Photo: MacLaren cemetery) : Diplomat Magazine
data.meta_description: Diplomat & International Canada magazine is Canada's leading source for international affairs and Canadian foreign policy. Diplomat is the magazine for people who want to stay informed about global issues and who care about Canada's role in the world. It is also a showcase for the diplomatic community in Canada.
